  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <span class="govuk-caption-xl gem-c-title__context">
      News story
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    1 million pensioners to benefit from £140 winter bill discount
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Around a million pensioners across the UK will receive £140 off their fuel bills thanks to Government efforts working with energy firms to cut their costs.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
    <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds metadata-column">
        <div class="app-c-publisher-metadata" lang="en">
    <div class="app-c-published-dates " lang="en">
    Published 14 October 2020
    <br></br>Last updated 14 October 2020
